org.springframework.scheduling.config

类 ScheduledTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.scheduling.config.ScheduledTask

  • public final class ScheduledTask
extends java.lang.Object
    A representation of a scheduled task at runtime, used as a return value for scheduling methods.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.3
    作者:
    Juergen Hoeller
    另请参阅:
    ScheduledTaskRegistrar.scheduleCronTask(CronTask), ScheduledTaskRegistrar.scheduleFixedRateTask(FixedRateTask), ScheduledTaskRegistrar.scheduleFixedDelayTask(FixedDelayTask)
